 4. Expressing Actions with Key Verbs
✅ Regular –ER Verbs
Conjugation Example: PARLER (to speak)

Subject	Conjugation
je	parle
tu	parles
il/elle	parle
nous	parlons
vous	parlez
ils/elles	parlent

📝 Other common –ER verbs:

aimer (to like/love), travailler (to work), étudier (to study), chanter (to sing), danser (to dance)

